Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社團晨練？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她倒是說過今天不用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是又跑羽佐間家去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天那之後我被媽媽罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要是害你遲到了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那點程度的 衝刺一下根本不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意這種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你看起來比昨天精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要咲良 上學去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 羽佐間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還是來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 肯定很快就能來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這書很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是坐今早的船回來的嗎 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在CDC寫報告 所以來遲了
